. O-O-O b5 13. Be2 Bg7 {[%csl Rd4] White's queen is totally out of the game here.} 14. Kb1 Bb7 15. Rhe1 Nd4 $10 {[%cal Gd8b6,Ge8c8]} ({Followed by ...Qb6 and long castle and we safeguard our king. Other options like} 15... Qe7 {and 15...Qd7 preparing long castle are also completely fine.}) *

