ve.} 18. fxe5 (18. Qxh4 Nf3+ {is the point.}) 18... Rxd4+ 19. Bxd4 Qxd4+ 20. Bd3 Nc6 21. Qe3 Qxe3+ 22. Kxe3 Nxe5 {[%csl Re3] Black is totally fine, thanks to the vulnerable white king and Black's active pieces.} *

