e d-file will be under the rook's control on [d1].} 9. dxc5 Nxc5 {[%csl Rc3,Gc5,Rd3,Gg7] Black's pieces have been activated, and now White's bishop on [d3] and the knight on [c3] are under pressure.} 10. Bxc5 Bxc3+ $1 {A nice intermezzo shattering White's pawn structure before capturing on [c5].} 11. bxc3 {[%csl Rc2,Rc3]} dxc5 12. e5 Nh6 {As the [f6]-square is not available, we head to [h6].} 13. e6 O-O 14. exf7+ Nxf7 $10 {Black has stabilized the game.} *

