knight on [f6] and the queen holds the [e5]-pawn at the same time.} 13. Qe1 Nh5 $10 {[%cal Gc8e6,Gc7c5] Next, Black can develop the [c8]-bishop to [e6] and also control the center with ...[c5].} ({The immediate} 13... Be6 {would allow unnecessary complications after} 14. d4 {since we cannot capture on [d4] in view of [e5].}) *

