counterplay idea, without which we would be crushed.} 9. Be4 Bxe4 10. Nxe4 cxd4 11. exd6 Ngf6 {We have coordinated our pieces.} 12. dxe7 Qxe7 13. Nxf6+ Nxf6 14. Re1 Ne4 15. Qd3 f5 {[%csl Ge4,Gf5] Sealing the knight on [e4], which restricts White's activity on the e-file.} 16. Ng5 O-O $10 {Finally, our king has founds its place. : All cool now.} *

