referred} 10... e5 {to keep some chances and went on to win a nice game. However, from a scientific and objective standpoint, 10...e5 is not the best move. The text move 10...exd5 , on the other hand, effectively solves Black's problems.}) 11. exd5 Re8 {Seizing control of the open e-file.} 12. Qd2 Nbd7 13. Rfe1 Nc5 $10 {[%cal Gc5e4,Gf6e4] Black's position remains solid, with ...[Ne4] coming to exchange one of the knights, which in turn activates the bishop on [g7].} *

