{Black to play.} 14... Ngxe5 $3 {Bam!!} 15. fxe5 Nxe5 {[%csl Rd3,Rf3]} 16. Nxe5 Bxe5 {[%csl Re1] Black has sacrificed the piece for two pawns, and our activity is just killing with constant threats around their king. Especially the bishops on [e5] and [b7] are just cruising into White's camp.} 17. O-O Qd5 {[%cal Gb7g2]} 18. Rf2 Rad8 {[%cal Gd8d1]} 19. Bf4 {The only counter move to save the piece.} c4 20. Bc2 Qc5 {[%cal Gc5g1]} 21. Qf1 b3 $15 {And it is White who has to be cautious here with all their pieces going backwards.} *

