{Black has to act quickly to change the dynamics of the game. How?} 16... Nd4 $1 {Black needs to act swiftly to generate counterplay; otherwise, the position could start crumbling. Precision and dynamic play are key here – waiting too long will allow White to seize control. Time to strike!} 17. Bxd4 exd4 18. Nb6 Ra7 $1 {[%csl Ga6,Ga7]} (18... Rb8 {loses contact over the [a6]-pawn after} 19. Nb4 {.}) 19. Nb4 Bb7 $132 {[%csl Re4] Black is holding on. The [e4]-pawn is hanging.} *

